outputs.output_descr: The project aims to reorient UNDP Timor-Leste's  programme and mainstream conflict-sensitivity; develop new initiatives to respond to emerging peace-building and recovery challenges; and integrate the crisis prevention and recovery dimension in the upcoming UNDAF and UNDP Country Programme 2008-2012.

project_descr: Preparatory Assistance - Crisis Prevention and Recovery  (CPR) Strategy for Timor-Leste
project_title: Preparatory Assistance - Crisis Prevention and Recovery
